msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho sāriputta. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn97:11.4"
msgid "Atha kho naṃ vikkandantaṃyeva niraye nirayapālā pakkhipeyyuṃ”. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: nya12, pts-vp-pli2.188, sc9
msgctxt "mn97:12.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, dhanañjāni, idhekacco pubbapetānaṃ hetu adhammacārī visamacārī assa, tamenaṃ adhammacariyāvisamacariyāhetu nirayaṃ nirayapālā upakaḍḍheyyuṃ. "
